{"word":"σφός","slug":"σφός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σφός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σφεῖς'><el>σφεῖς</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>poetic for <a href='S:σφέτερος'><el>σφέτερος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>their, their own, belonging to them</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in sg. <i>his</i> or <i>her, his own</i> or <i>her own</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}